author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Cad It Announces Provisional Results Of Tender Offer By Quarantacinque
text:
April 9 (Reuters) - CAD IT:
* SAID ON FRIDAY 4.7 MLN SHARES WERE TENDERED TO QUARANTACINQUE S.R.L (THE OFFEROR) EQUAL TO 52.018% OF CAD IT SHARE CAPITAL
* SHARES WERE TENDERED FOR TOTAL EUR 24.8 MLN * AS A RESULT, THE OFFEROR WILL OWN – IF PROVISIONAL RESULTS ARE CONFIRMED – A TOTAL OF 5.9 MLN SHARES, CORRESPONDING TO 66.252% CAD IT CAPITAL
